Class RexBiVisitorImpl<R,P>

java.lang.Object
org.apache.calcite.rex.RexBiVisitorImpl<R,P>
Type Parameters:

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
RexUnaryBiVisitor
public class RexBiVisitorImpl<@Nullable R,P> extends Object implements RexBiVisitor<R,P>
Default implementation of RexBiVisitor, which visits each node but does nothing while it's there.
